},{"label":"Heating"},{"label":"Dishwasher"},{"label":"Oven"},{"label":"Refrigerator"},{"label":"Teak Side Decks"},{"label":"Gangway"}],"toys":[{"label":"Water Ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wake Board","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Paddle Board","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Ringo","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Amateur Snorkeling Equipment","quantity":"3"},{"label":"Amateur Fishing Equipment","quantity":"3"}],"entertainment":["Internet","DVD","Music Player"],"tenders":[]},"crew":[{"name":"Mesut Güvercinoğlu","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bc05bc20-1e89-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I’m Mesut, your second captain on board. I've been working as a captain for 13 years now. I graduated from Ekol Maritime University with a degree in Deck Management and Operations in 2011. Later, I pursued a degree in International Trade at Eskisehir University and graduated in 2016.\nThroughout my career, I’ve gained extensive experience in various maritime Rields. I’m particularly skilled in scuba diving, boat maintenance, and sailing instruction. I’m passionate about what I do and always strive to offer the best service possible. Additionally, I’m Rluent in both Turkish and English, so communication is never an issue."},{"name":"Ufuk Edinsel","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c5269e50-1e89-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Greetings, I am Ufuk, born in 1974, and I bring over a decade of experience in the maritime sector, commencing my career in 2010. As a dedicated professional, I am entrusted with the responsibility of ensuring the seamless operation of voyages and facilitating safe passage to your desired destinations. With a comprehensive array of certifications pertinent to the maritime domain, I am committed to upholding the highest standards of safety, efficiency, and reliability throughout our journey together. My aim is to deliver excellence and peace of mind to all passengers under my care."},{"name":"Eren Ürer","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d9e48640-1e89-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"After a 10-year career as a bartender, including 8 years in Istanbul and 2 years in Gö cek, I decided to pursue a new path in the maritime industry. I have experience in sailing Optimist, Laser, 4.20-4.70 classes as a member of the Istanbul Yacht Club. I am open to self- improvement, possess strong communication skills, and work well in a team. I am proRicient in English in speaking, reading, and writing and ı have intermediate knowledge of italian for service"},{"name":"Naime Ümran Güleray","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::edf0f880-1e89-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I’m Naime, the chef on board. I was born in Istanbul in 1959 and have been pursuing my career as a chef since 1992. I’ve worked on large ships and on land, bringing a wealth of experience to our kitchen.\nCooking is a great pleasure for me, and it’s our duty to ensure you and your loved ones have the best possible experience during your holiday. I’m here to delight you with delicious meals and make your stay unforgettable.\nLooking forward to serving you!"},{"name":"Irmak Işılak","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f4ee1050-1e89-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I’m Irmak, your stewardess on board. While this is my first year working at sea, I have 8 years of experience in this field on land. I'm a very hardworking person, and I have a deep passion for maritime safety, supported by numerous certifications.\nI’m fluent in both Turkish and English, so communication is always smooth. My love for the sea and commitment to providing excellent service drives me to ensure you have a safe and enjoyable journey.\nLooking forward to serving you on this voyage!"},{"name":"Ertuğrul Bayram","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7580644139::vessel::d5cc24f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0620aea0-1e8a-11ef-93c8-2b3ea6ebc4cc.jpeg/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I am an experienced maritime professional with a career spanning since 2017, specializing in deck maintenance, repairs, and water sports. Holding various certi@ications including speedboat operation, @irst aid, safety awareness, and @ire prevention, I am committed to ensuring the safety and enjoyment of all passengers.\nBeyond my technical expertise, my dedication lies in curating exceptional maritime experiences. Whether it's navigating the open seas or engaging in water sports activities, I am devoted to delivering excellence and professionalism at every turn. Join me onboard for a voyage characterized by safety, comfort, and the promise of unforgettable memories"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2750000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2750000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3250000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3250000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"April, May & October & June","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2024-03-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2024-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-03-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-03-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2024-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2024-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2750000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2750000,"amount":2750000,"conditions":"per week + all expenses","taxRate":{"l